      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should check with my doctor but the clinic is closed until monday and i honestly cant handle the pain right now. i just want to know if it's actually dangerous for the baby or if it's just a precaution. i've taken it before and was totally fine, so i just want to know if it's actually an issue or if it's just standard stuff.",
