      "role": "user",
      "content": "ugh okay fine. if i can't do the antibiotic then can i at least take some Sudafed? i have some pseudoephedrine tablets in my medicine cabinet. i read online that it's fine for most people to use if they're just really congested. is that okay to take just for tonight so i can actually sleep?",
